                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <h4>Try to walk on their shoes</h4>
                    <p>The world is a place with more than seven million human beings living all together and 9.2 percent of them has to survive in extreme poverty conditions, struggling with the lack of economy incomes, health care and being completely vulnerable to  every threat that exist by living in this conditions. </p>
                    <p>In order to these statements the United Nations Organization has released a list of the sustainable development goals, and has established poverty as the main problem that the world is facing at the moment.</p>
                </div>
